race.description: Tabtouch Have You Got The Touch Hcp (C5)
race.comment: COVERT ROSE (1) had her chance last start when beaten in a photo finish at this track and trip. She may have felt the pinch late second-up when failing to reel in the leader and looks primed third-up into the campaign. Can raise the bar now and go one better. WORCESTER (3) was only 0.3L off the winner last start at Belmont when jumping the race fav. He too was given a great run in transit and has the speed to work across from the draw today. Looks to main danger on recent ratings. I'M NIPOTE (5) was very impressive first-up over an unsuitable trip and looks beautifully placed up to the mile. He boasts a good second-up record and Fiore knows him well. Can land in a handy position and land the knockout blow. SKETTA (9) is not out of this from what we've seen recently and the 3kg claim comes in handy. MAJOR MARIO (2) is racing well and can improve again now out to the mile.
